titles.title: Cape Fox Land Entitlement Finalization Act of 2025
Cape Fox Land Entitlement Finalization Act of 2025
A bill to provide equitable treatment for the people of the Village Corporation established for the Native Village of Saxman, Alaska, and for other purposes.

action.text: Introduced in the Senate. Read the first time. Placed on Senate Legislative Calendar under Read the First Time.

calendar.text: Read the second time. Placed on Senate Legislative Calendar under General Orders. Calendar No. 28.
